---
title: Lemongrass Pork Coconut Curry with Butternut Squash, Spinach and Naan
description: There are some flavour combinations that are hard to beat – lemongrass and coconut milk is one of them! Butternut squash further enhances the sweetness from these flavour-makers and the cilantro-lime rice brings everything together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemongrass-pork-coconut-curry-962707ef.jpg
